OL,4,CEvery childhood vaccine in a single jab
OL,5, A technology that could eventually see
OL,6, every childhood vaccine delivered in a
OL,7, single injection has been developed by
OL,8, US researchers. 
OL,10,FTheir one-shot solution stores the
OL,11,Fvaccine in microscopic capsules that
OL,12,Frelease the initial dose and then
OL,13,Fboosters at specific times. 
OL,15,FThe approach has been shown to work in
OL,16,Fmouse studies, described in the journal
OL,17,FScience. 
OL,19,FThe researchers say the technology
OL,20,Fcould help patients around the world. 
